title: President Trump Calls - H3 After Dark #28
description: On this episode of H3 After Dark we get a call in from our illustrious former president, Donald J Trump. We also speak with the CEO of Kraken, a crypto exchange, and collector of NFTs who is trying to complete the H3 Podcast Exodia. We also check out some insane TikToks including Ethan's new favorite guy- Whiteclaw Gabe! Also fartgate 2.0 with Windy Williams, guys this is a jam packed episode you won't want to miss!
